name: Froge
description: Froge is a memecoin based on the Froge character which refers to a set of Discord emotes of a worried frog expressing various emotions. The frog image comes from the now-inactive mobile game Froge, released in 2014 by Fandom Inc. and became popularized as a set of Discord emotes starting in 2020. In 2023, a Froge ChatGPT plugin launched and is now OpenAI's unofficial mascot.
